#: ../animation.rst:23
msgid "Animation"
msgstr ""

#: ../animation.rst:25
msgid "OpenShot has been designed specifically with animation in mind. The powerful curve-based animation framework can handle most jobs with ease, and is flexible enough to create just about any animation. Key frames specify values at certain points on a clip, and OpenShot does the hard work of interpolating the in-between values."
msgstr ""

